    "crit": 16,
    "description": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Nirvana is a chewable orange solid sold commercially in even the smallest magecraft supply store and goes by a multitude of tradenames. A character may chew a lozenge for a +25 bonus to their Mental Limit, and a 1d3 penalty to their DEX modifier and Will Saving Throw. The effect lasts for 8 hours. When a character has spells, powers, or invocations that currently occupy the bonus Mental Limit when the effect ends, they immediately lose at least 15 Mental Limit worth of spells, invocations, and powers, chosen at random by the GM. If they chew another lozenge again, they regain these lost spells, powers and invocations. Nirvana is packaged in 10 piece packs.</span> <br style=\" font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \"></p>"
